quran[52]{c,v,t}:
  14,1,"Alif, Laam, Raa. (Ndee ko) Deftere nde Men jippini e maa…óa, fii yo yaltinir yim…ďe …ďen e ni…ďe faade e annoora, e duŇčayee Joomi ma…ď…ďe, haa e laawol Foolu…óo, Yettinii…óo"
  14,2,"Alla, On Mo woodani kala ko woni kammuuli e ka leydi. Bone woodani yeddu…ďe …ďen, immorde e lepte sattu…óe"
  14,3,"∆Āen …ďurdinoo…ďe nguurndam aduna …óam e dow laakara, …ďe faddoo e laawol Alla ngol, …ďe …óa…ď…ďana ngol oo√Īorgal. ∆Āen …óow wonii e majjere wo…ó…óunde"
  14,4,"Men nuliraali Nulaa…óo (woo), si wanaa e …óemngal yim…ďe makko …ďen, fii no o …ďannginirana …ďe. Alla no majjina on Mo muuyi, O fewna on Mo O muuyi. Ko Kanko woni Foolu…óo, √Ďee√Īu…óo"
  14,5,"Gom…óii Men nulirii Muusaa Aayeeje Amen …óen [wi'ugol Mo]: \"Yaltin yim…ďe maa …ďen e ni…ďe faade e annoora, anndintinaa …ďe √Īal…ói Alla …óin\". Pellet hino e …óum, tasakuyeeji kala munyoowo, yettoowo (neema)"
  14,6,"(Janto) tuma nde Muusaa maakannoo yim…ďe makko …ďen: \"siftoree neema Alla on e moo…óon, tuma O da…óndunoo on e yim…ďe Fir'awna …ďe no defaynoo on lepte bon…óe. Hi…ďe hirsa …ďi…ó…ďe mon (wor…ďe) …ďe acca (…ďi…ó…ďe) mon rew…ďe. Wonii e …óum mo'on, jarrabuyee maw…óo immorde ka Joomi mon"
  14,7,"e tuma nde Joomi maa anndinnoo: \"Pellet si on yettii, ma Mi …ďeydan on. Si on yeddii non, pellet lepte am …óen ko sa…ótu…óe"
  14,8,"Muusaa maaki: \"Si on yeddii, onon e won…ďe ka leydi …ďen fow, [anndon] pellet Alla ko Galo Yettinii…óo"
  14,9,"E kumpite …ďen adinoo…ďe on araali on, yim…ďe Nuuhu e Aadi, e Samuuda e …ďen wonunoo…ďe …ďaawo ma…ď- …ďe, anndaa …ďe si wanaa Alla? Nulaa…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen addanii …ďe …ďanngannduyeeji, …ďe rutti juu…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen ka kunndule ma…ď…ďe, …ďe wi'i: \"Menen men yed- dii ko nulida…óon e mun kon, menen, me…óen e sikkitii e ko noddoton men e mun sikkitii…ďe"
  14,10,"Nulaa…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen maaki: \"E hara sikke no e fii Alla, fu…ó…óu…óo kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin, himo nodda on fii yo O haforan on yoga e junuubi mon, himo nennana on haa e lajal innaangal?\" ∆Āe wi'i: \"On wonaali si wanaa …ďanndinke yeru amen. Hi…óon faandii nde sakkoto…óon(falotodon) men e kon ko baabiraa…ďe amen rewaynoo. Addanee men hujja …ďanngu…óo"
  14,11,"Nulaa…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen maakani …ďe: \"[Ko goonga], men wonaali si wanaa …ďanndinke yeru mon, kono Alla no mo∆ī∆īoo e Mo O muuyi e jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďen. Laatanaaki men nde men addana on hujja, si wanaa e duŇčayee Alla. Ko e Alla gom…óim…ďe …ďen fawotoo"
  14,12,"Ko ha…óata men nde fawotoo e Alla, gom…óii O fewnii men (e) laawi amen? Ma men mu√Ī√Īo e kon ko lorroton men. Ko e Alla gom…óim…ďe …ďen fawotoo"
  14,13,"∆Āen yeddu…ďe (kadi) wi'ani Nulaa…ďe mun …ďen: \"Ma men yaltin on ka leydi amen, maa rutto…óon e diina amen\". Joomi ma…ď…ďe wahayini e ma…ď…ďe: \"Ma men halku too√Īu…ďe …ďen"
  14,14,"Ma Men ho…ónu on e leydi ndin …ďaawo ma…ď…ďe. ∆äum ko wonannde on hulu…óo daroyagol yeeso Am, o huli kammbaa Am on"
  14,15,∆Āe …óa…ď…ďi uddital. Sooyi kala dunndaranke ∆īaggu…óo
  14,16,"Jahannama no yesso makko, himo yarniree ndiyam mbordi ∆īii∆īiiri"
  14,17,"himo woo…ďa …óam, e …óe…ďataa …ďennugol …óam. Maayde nden ardana mo e kala nokku, kono o wonaali maayoowo. Hara no yeeso makko lepte sattu…óe"
  14,18,"Ko woni sifa …ďen yeddu…ďe Joomi mun, kuu…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen, ko wano ndoondi ndi henndu tii…ói e mun, e √Īalaande wippoore. ∆Āe hettoytaa huunde e ko …ďe faggitinoo. Ko …óum woni majjere won…ó…óunde"
  14,19,"E a yi'aali Alla tagirii kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin goonga? Si O muuyii, O ittay on O adda tagu hesu"
  14,20,…óum wonaali sattu…óum ka Alla
  14,21,"∆Āe fee√Īana Alla …ďe denndaangal. Lo'u…ďe …ďen wi'ana townitinoo…ďe …ďen: \"Menen men wonanno on jokku…ďe. Taw si on duncanay men e lepte Alla …óen go…ó…óum?\" ∆Āen wi'a: \"Sinno Alla fewnuno men, men fewnayno on. Hino fota e amen, si en …óen∆īi maa si en mu√Ī√Īi; da…óirde alanaa en"
  14,22,"Seytaane wi'a, tuma fiyaaku on √Īaawaa: \"Pellet Alla fodiino on fodoore goonga; mi fodi on mi lunndii on. Alanaa lam e mo'on immorde e hujja, si wanaa mi nodii on, on jaabike lam. Wata on felam; felee ko'e mon. Wanaa mi faabotoo…óo on; wanaa on faabotoo…ďe lam. Mi yeddii ko kafiduno…óon mi kon [e Alla] ado (hannde)\". Pellet, too√Īoo…ďe …ďen, hino woodani …ďe lepte muusu…óe"
  14,23,"Gom…óim…ďe golli mo∆ī∆īu…ói …ďen naatnaa e Aljannaaji, can…ói hino ila ley majji, ko …ďe duumoray…ďe ton e duŇčayee Joomi ma…ď…ďe. Hiwraandu ma…ď…ďe ndun ton ko: \"Salaam\" (Kisiyee). @Corrected"
  14,24,"E a yi'aali ko honno Alla piyiri misal konngol laa…ďungol, ko wano leggal welngal, binndeere maggal ko tabitu…ói, cal…ói maggal no ka weeyo"
  14,25,"Hingal okkira dim…óe maggal on tuma kala, e duŇčayee Joomi maggal. Alla no piyana yim…ďe …ďen mise, belajo'o …ďe waajitoto"
  14,26,"Ko woni kadi misal konngol so…ďungol, ko wano leggal so…ďungal, irtaangal ka hoore-leydi, ngal alanaa …óum √Īii…ďirde"
  14,27,"Alla no tabintinira gom…óim…ďe …ďen konngol tabitungol, ka nguurandam aduna e ka laakara. Alla no majjina too√Īoo…ďe …ďen. Alla no wa…óa ko O muuyi"
  14,28,"E a tinaali …ďen wa…ótitir…ďe neemaaji Alla …óin keeferaaku, …ďe weerni yim…ďe …ďen galle halkaare"
  14,29,"Jahannama, hi…ďe naata nge, nge bonii √Īii…ďirde"
  14,30,"∆Āe wa…óani Alla yerondiraa…ói fii yo …ďe majjin (yim…ďe …ďen) e laawol Alla ngol. Maaku: \"Dakmitee, pellet ruttorde mon nden ko ka Yiite"
  14,31,"Maakan jeyaa…ďe am gom…óim…ďe …ďen, yo …ďe √Īinnu julde …ďe wintoo e kon ko Men arsiki …ďe gunndoo e kene, ado nde arata …ďe √Īalaande nde jgeeygu alaa e mun wanaa weldigal"
  14,32,"Ko Alla woni tagu…óo kammuuli …óin e leydi, O jippiniri ka kammu ndiyam; O yaltiniri …óam dim…óe arsike wonannde on. O eltirani on laa…óe …óen, fii yo …óe dogir ka maayo e duŇčayee Makko. O eltani on kadi can…ói …óin"
  14,33,O eltani on naange ngen e lewru ndun dogooji …ói…ói. O eltani on jemma on e √Īalorma on
  14,34,"O okki on e kala ko tori…óon Mo. Si on lintii neemaaji Alla …óin, on moftataa…ói. Pellet ne…ó…óanke on ko hee- wu…óo too√Īe, heewu…óo yeddugol"
  14,35,"(Janto) kadi tuma nde Ibraahiima maakunoo: \"Joomi am, wa…óu ndee saare hooliinde, da…óndaa lam e …ďi…ó…ďe am …ďen nde men rewata sanamuuji"
  14,36,"Joomi am, kannji (sanamuuji …óin), …ói majjinii ko …óuu…ói e yim…ďe …ďen. Kala jokku…óo lam, on …óon ko jeyidaa…óo e am. Kala non yeddu…óo lam, haray An ko A Haforoowo, Hinnotoo…óo"
  14,37,"Joomi amen, min mi ho…óinii yoga e …ďi…ó…ďe am …ďen e aynde nde wonaa remotoonde, ka Suudu Maa Hormanteeru, - Joomi amen - fii yo …ďe √Īinnu julde. Wa…óu …ďer…óe yim…ďe …ďen no yiiloo e ma…ď…ďe, arsikaa…ďe dim…óe, belajo'o …ďe yetta"
  14,38,"Joomi amen, pellet, An hi…óa anndi ko men suu…ói e ko men fe√Ī√Īini: hay huunde suu…óotaako Alla ka leydi wanaa ka kammu"
  14,39,"Yettoore woodanii Alla, On ye…óu…óo lam e hoore mawngu, Ismaa'iila e Ishaaqa. Pellet, Joomi am ko nanoowo du'aa"
  14,40,"Joomi am, wa…óan √Īinnoowo julde e …ďeynugol am ngol. Joomi amen, ja…ďu toraare am nden"
  14,41,"Joomi amen, haforanam min e jibim…ďe lam …ďen e gom…óim…ďe …ďen, √Īalnde √Īaawoore nden dorotoo"
  14,42,"Wata sikku Alla ko welsindii…óo e ko too√Īoo…ďe …ďen huuwata. Anndu ko O nenniranta …ďe, ko haa e √Īalaande nde gite saafotoo e mun"
  14,43,"Ko …ďe he√Īii…ďe, Ňčallim…ďe ko'e ma…ď…ďe, ndaar…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen yiltotaako e ma…ď…ďe, …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen ko yeewu…óe"
  14,44,"Jertniri yim…ďe …ďen √Īalaande nde lepte …óen arata …ďe, too√Īu…ďe …ďen wi'a: \"Joomi amen, nennan men haa lajal …ďa…óiingal, men nootoo noddaanndu Maa, men jokka Nulaa…ďe …ďen\". E on laatanooki on woondiino ado (hannde) alanaa on iwugol (ton)"
  14,45,"Ho…óu…óon e ko…óooli …ďen too√Īu…ďe ko'e mun. ∆Āanngani on ko honno Men huuwunoo …ďe, Men piyani on mise"
  14,46,"Gom…óii …ďe fewjii feere ma…ď…ďe nden. Ko ka Alla feere ma…ď…ďe nden woni, hay si feere ma…ď…ďe nden ittayno pelle …óen"
  14,47,"Wata a sikku Alla ko lunndotoo…óo fodoore Makko (nde O fodi) Nulaa…ďe Makko …ďen. Pellet, Alla ko Foolu…óo, Jom yottagol"
  14,48,"√Īalnde leydi ndin wa…ótitirtee leydi goo, e kammuuli …óin, …ďe fee√Īana Alla, Bajjo On, Foolu…óo On"
  14,49,"A yi'ay bom…ďe …ďen nden √Īalnde, ko jokkindiraa…ďe e kolombooje"
  14,50,"Dolokkaaji ma…ď…ďe …óin ko mbullam feewnira, Yiite ngen no sudda geece ma…ď…ďe …óen"
  14,51,"Fii yo Alla yo…ďitu kala wonkii ko ko faggitii. Pellet, Alla ko yaawu…óo hasboore"
  14,52,"Ndee (Alqur'aanaare) ko yottinoore yim…ďe …ďen fii yo …ďe waajitornde, e yo…ďe anndu kadi, wonnde Kanko ko O rewetee…óo Gooto, e fii yo joomiraa…ďe haqqillaaji …ďen waajitor"